articles.author: Audrey Conklin, Julia Bonavita
articles.title: UNC fraternity brothers defend reinstated American flag from campus mob who replaced with Palestinian flag - Fox News
articles.description: UNC-Chapel Hill students on Tuesday stopped an American flag on campus, which anti-Israel protesters had previously replaced with a Palestinian flag, from hitting the ground.
articles.content:
FIRST ON FOX: A moment of patriotism on the University of North Carolina-Chapel Hill campus Tuesday has captured the nation's attention.
